    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped out per ASME V&V 40 Table 3 requirements for Class II devices at MRL 2. Experimental validation demonstrates CFD predictions within acceptance criterion (max 9.1% deviation vs. 15% threshold). Mesh convergence confirmed (GCI 2.07%). Uncertainty quantification completed for mesh, experimental comparison, and sensitivity analysis validation activities. The compound credibility evidence is judged sufficient to support regulatory submission for the CPB hemolysis indication.",
